                            <comment id="19051" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Mon, 14 Aug 2006 11:41:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Indeed, I agree - I have reverted this change for 2.0 final, &lt;b&gt;not&lt;/b&gt; inheriting the parent&apos;s ClassLoader by default. Since we still do have the &quot;getClassLoader()&quot; method on the ApplicationContext interface, it&apos;s easy enough for whoever assembles the child context to also set the parent&apos;s ClassLoader explicitly there.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
